- GA4 custom dimension `landing_variant` is set on every event via `gtag('set', { 'landing_variant': 'v1'|'v2' })`. **Already registered in GA4 admin** May 6 2026 — name "Landing Variant", scope Event, parameter `landing_variant`. Data is flowing; standard reports populate it within 24–48h of registration.
